(lp15
VFinancial support for this study was provided by the Instituto Nacional
p16
aVde Ecologia y Cambio Climatic (INECC) as part of a long-term project
p17
aV"MARCO AMBIENTAL DE LAS CONDICIONES OCEANOGRAFICAS EN EL SECTOR NW DE LA
p18
aVZEE DE MEXICO EN EL GOLFO DE MEXICO (MARZEE)." The authors express their
p19
aVgratitude to the crew members of the "R/V Justo Sierra" and the
p20
aVscientific party that participated in this project. Thanks are also
p21
aVextended to Claudia E. Garcia-Ruelas and Francisco Rivera-Ramirez for
